{
.appVersion = "983";
DisplayStrings = (
"Aussenwirkung\012Blocksatz\012Cauda\012Durchschuss\012Einzelblatt\012F\U00E4hnchen\012Grundlinie\012Hurenkind\012Industrienorm\012Jungfrau\012Kopfzeile\012Linksb\U00FCndig\012Monatsbl\U00E4tter\012Nachbreite\012Oberl\U00E4nge\012Paginierung\012Querstrich\012Rotunda\012Spationierung\012Typografie\012Unterl\U00E4nge\012Versalh\U00F6he\012Werkschrift\012X-h\U00F6he\012YCC\012Zeilenabstand\012Br",
"A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart. I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so happy, my dear friend, so absorbed in the exquisite sense of mere tranquil existence, that I neglect my talents. I should be incapable of drawing a single stroke at the present moment",
"EXQUISITE\012CONSPIRACY\012MONOCHROME\012OCTOCHAMP\012OVERRATED\012EINE NEUE\012HHGHIH\012KIMONO\012NEW KIDS SON\012CHEESE CSS CSS\012THE BLOCK\012ETERNITY\012KILLERGRAM\012RADAR RADIO\012KILLERGRAM\012JUICY J\012STUCK\012CALVIN \012KLEIN \012HHKHH\012JEANS\012MOMENTUM\012Moda\012",
